{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-index-tsx","path":"/post/shiyong-wsl-anzhuang-nvm","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>安装NVM</h2>\n<p>使用Root或者常用的用户</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 移动至安装目录</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> /usr/local\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 新建文件夹</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> nvm\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 移动至src文件夹</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> src\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/creationix/nvm.git</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>编辑<code class=\"language-text\">~/.bashrc</code>文件</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">vim</span> ~/.bashrc</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>在里面追加</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">NVM_DIR</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/usr/local/nvm\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> /usr/src/nvm/nvm.sh</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>然后重新登录后验证下</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nvm --version</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>正常输出就没问题</p>\n<h2>安装NodeJS</h2>\n<p>查看可安装的NodeJS版本</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nvm -ls-remote</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>安装稳定版本<code class=\"language-text\">12.16.3</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nvm <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token number\">12.16</span>.3</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>安装常用的Yarn包</h2>\n<p>安装<code class=\"language-text\">yarn</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> -g i <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>然后进入项目重新安装一次项目</p>\n<h2>设置代理</h2>\n<p>有时候可能会用到代理</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">alias</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">socks</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'ALL_PROXY=socks5://127.0.0.1:1080/ \\\n        http_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:1080/ \\\n        https_proxy=http://127.0.0.1:1080/ \\\n        HTTP_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:1080/ \\\n        HTTPS_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:1080/'</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","id":"65cf1dc8-9ea7-5eb7-b803-7ee46f171eba","fields":{"title":"使用WSL安装NVM","tags":["debian","nodejs"],"category":"记录","date":"2020-05-05T18:48:00+08:00","dateModified":"2020-05-06T17:32:33+08:00","slug":"/post/shiyong-wsl-anzhuang-nvm","status":true,"comment":true},"excerpt":"安装NVM 使用Root…"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/post/shiyong-wsl-anzhuang-nvm","prev":{"slug":"/post/kaifa-yige-zhongduan-dongtai-duohang-shuchu-de-gongju","title":"开发一个终端动态多行输出的工具","date":"2020-04-01T14:03:00+08:00","category":"记录","tags":["nodejs"],"type":"post"},"next":null}}}